      • theNextStep

        public java.util.ArrayList<Geom.Point3D> theNextStep()
        This function calculate the next path which the player would go. At first, the function will check if the target is Fruit or Packman. After that, There are 2 options: [-1-] the packman will go stright to the target: [-2-] the packman need to ass through obstacles in order to reach the goal.
        Returns:
        The current packman's path.
